      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "顯要之人。《呂氏春秋．勸學》曰：「不疾學而能為天下魁士名人者，未之嘗有也。」高誘《注》：「名德之人。」",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-15",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 103,
        "end": 105
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "與：從也。遊：友也，交遊也。《禮記．曲禮》曰：「交遊稱其信也。」又《禮記．學記》曰：「息焉遊焉。」《註》曰：「遊，謂無事閒暇總在於學也。」《論語．里仁》曰：「遊必有方。」與遊：跟從交往，追隨學習也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-16",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 107,
        "end": 108
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "行也，走也。今謂之捷步。《釋名》曰：「疾行曰趨。」此謂往赴之意。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-17",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 112,
        "end": 121
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "先達：有學問道德之前輩，因先我聞道，故曰先達。《明史．宋濂傳》曰：「幼英敏強記，就學於聞人夢吉，通《五經》，復往從吳萊學。已，游柳貫、黃溍之門。」執：持也。執經：手持經書，意謂從師受業。叩：問也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-18",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 124,
        "end": 128
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "亦作德高望重。指年高德劭者。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-19",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 133,
        "end": 134
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "《說文》曰：「塞也。」滿也。擠滿之意。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-20",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 139,
        "end": 143
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "稍：漸也。降：抑也。謙抑之意。辭：言辭。色：神色。猶和顏悅色。此言謙恭受教。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-21",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 150,
        "end": 154
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "援：《說文》曰：「引也。」疑：疑問也。質：《廣雅》曰：「問也。」理：道理也。此言提問之意。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-22",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 155,
        "end": 161
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "俯身：彎腰貌。傾：側也。傾耳：側耳靜聽。《史記．淮陰侯列傳》曰：「農夫莫不輟耕釋耒，褕衣甘食，傾耳以待命者。」請：問也。《禮記．曲禮》曰：「請業則起，請益則起。」意謂恭敬聆聽，虛心受教。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-23",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 165,
        "end": 167
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "大聲呼喝斥責。咄：粵音doet1；漢音duō。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-24",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 168,
        "end": 171
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "色：容色也。恭：敬也。意謂態度更加恭敬。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-25",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 0,
        "start": 184,
        "end": 188
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "俟：候也。忻：同「欣」，悅貌。意謂等到老師高興的時候。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-26",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 6,
        "end": 10
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "負：背也，置項背也。篋：書箱也，粵音狹，haap6；漢音qiè。曳：拉、拖也。屣：鞋履也，粵音徙，saai2；漢音xǐ。言求學之艱辛也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-27",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "君；gwan1",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-28",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "jūn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-29",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 30,
        "end": 32
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "皸：凍裂也。皸裂：皮膚暴露風霜，寒凍而破裂。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-30",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 41,
        "end": 43
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "僵硬也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-31",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 47,
        "end": 49
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "認；jing6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-32",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 47,
        "end": 49
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "yìng",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-33",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 47,
        "end": 49
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "媵：陪嫁女。媵人：泛指家僕。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-34",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 49,
        "end": 53
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "湯：《說文》曰：「熱水也。」沃：以水洗手。灌：通「盥」，洗也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-35",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 54,
        "end": 58
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "衾：《說文》曰：「大被。」段玉裁《注》曰：「寢衣為小被（夾被），則衾是大被（棉被）。」擁覆：蓋上也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-36",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 64,
        "end": 67
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "寓：《說文》曰：「寄也。」寄居之意。逆旅：客舍、旅館。杜預《注》曰：「逆旅，客舍也。」",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-37",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 70,
        "end": 73
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "再食：兩頓飯。意謂旅舍每日祇供應兩頓飯。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-38",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 86,
        "end": 89
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "被：穿著也。綺繡：彩色絲織品。意謂穿著綾羅綢緞。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-39",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 91,
        "end": 93
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "朱：大紅色。纓：帽帶。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-40",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 110,
        "end": 112
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "臭：香氣。《易繫辭》曰：「同心之言，其臭如蘭。」容臭：猶香囊。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-41",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 113,
        "end": 118
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "業；jip6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-42",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 113,
        "end": 118
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "yè",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-43",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 113,
        "end": 118
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "燁：火盛明亮貌。神人：猶神仙。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-44",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 120,
        "end": 124
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "溫；wan1",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-45",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 120,
        "end": 124
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "yùn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-46",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 120,
        "end": 124
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "縕：亂絮也，以新棉合舊絮。敝：敗絮破衣，貧者所服也。《論語．子罕》曰：「子曰：衣敝縕袍，與衣狐貉者立，而不恥者，其由也與？」",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-47",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 143,
        "end": 145
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "口腹也。《孟子．離婁上》：「此所謂養口體者也。」",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-48",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 163,
        "end": 165
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "務；mou6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-49",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 163,
        "end": 165
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "mào",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-50",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 163,
        "end": 165
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "耄：年老之意。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-51",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 184,
        "end": 186
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "恩寵光耀。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-52",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 187,
        "end": 188
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "最；zeoi3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-53",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 187,
        "end": 188
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "zhuì",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-54",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 187,
        "end": 188
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "連也。追隨貌。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-55",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 193,
        "end": 196
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "每日侍奉於帝座之旁。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-56",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 197,
        "end": 200
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "備：待用也。顧問：供帝王諮詢之大臣。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-57",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 1,
        "start": 201,
        "end": 209
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "四海：言天下也。謬：誤也，欺也。稱：譽揚也。氏：姓也。此語謙謂自己名聞天下。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-58",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 5,
        "end": 7
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "古代之最高學府，即國學。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-59",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "凜；lam5",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-60",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "lǐn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-61",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "糧食、俸祿。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-62",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 25
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "惠；wai6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-63",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 25
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "wèi",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-64",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 25
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "裘：冬衣。葛：夏衣。泛指四時衣服。遺：餽贈也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-65",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 40,
        "end": 42
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "詩：《詩經》。書：《尚書》。泛指儒家經典。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-66",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 51,
        "end": 53
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "學官名。隋以後國子監置司業，為副長官，協助祭酒，掌儒學訓導之政。清末始廢。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-67",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 54,
        "end": 56
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "學官名，教官也。六國時置博士，秦因之。唐有太學博士、算學博士等，皆教授官。明清仍之。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-68",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 94,
        "end": 95
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "借也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-69",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 95,
        "end": 96
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "「之於」合音。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-70",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 12,
        "end": 17
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "質：本也，體也。天質：猶天份也。句意謂並非天資之低下。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-71",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "位於浙江省中部、浙東丘陵之邊緣地帶。元代屬婺州路。即今浙江省金華市轄下東陽市。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-72",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 14,
        "end": 16
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "同輩也。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-73",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 22,
        "end": 25
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "潮；ciu4",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "143-74",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
